<!---------------------------->
<table cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Recommended Level<br>for starting quest:</b></td><td valign="bottom"> 60<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting zone:</b></td><td valign="top"> Plane of Knowledge<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Additional zones:</b></td><td valign="top"> Plane of Tactics (Drunder, Fortress of Zek) and Bastion of Thunder<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting NPC:</b></td><td valign="top"> Gwiraba Gelrid<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Reward:</b></td><td valign="top"> Advanced Combat Manual<br><br></td></tr>
</table>

This is the last of three Combat Manuals.  To do this, you must have completed the first two.<br>
<Br>
You say, 'Hail, Gwiraba Gelrid' <br>
<Br>
Gwiraba Gelrid says 'Good day to you, Furioso. By the looks of things you have learned quite a bit about planar combat already, but if you wish to be truly knowledgeable on the subject, there is one last course you must undertake. Using your newfound courage and bravery, you must collect for me a Sandstorm Gem, a Rage Filled Gem, and a Blue Diamond. Bring me these items along with your Intermediate Combat Manual. And remember, unless you have the moral nerve to live out your convictions, they are of little account.'<br>
<Br>
Blue Diamonds can generally be round rarely on any high level monster.<Br>
<br>
Sandstorm Gems drop from the sand type giants (Jords) in the Bastion of Thunder.<br>
<br>
A Rage Filled Gem comes from named enemies in Drunder, Fortress of Zek (aka Plane of Tactics).  It may also drop from non-named NPCs, but I haven't seen any reports of this yet.<br>
<br>
Once you have all three gems, head back to Gwiraba Gelrid (I don't know where he is exactly) and hand him the gems and your Intermediate Combat Manual.  And there you have it, an Advanced Combat Manual.<br>
<Br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP  <br>
AC: +15 Str: +12 Sta: +12 HP: +35 Mana: +35  <br>
Weight: 1.0 <br>
Classes: All Classes  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
Inventory Slot: Secondary Range<br>

